      <ownedComment xmi:id="c3510d19-c568-49a2-84ec-118ae82b720a" body="A boundary is a class that lies on the periphery of a system, but within it. It interacts with actors outside the system as well as with entity, control, and other boundary classes within the system." annotatedElement="eeb2de9b-899c-4d18-a6b6-8949fb9c057c">
