        <ownedComment xmi:id="edf3e58a-0893-4a02-b825-cdd6b9c3ac29" body="This option determines whether contents of this smart package should be calculated and taken into account when operating in various Select Element dialogs. Having this option on may help you to pick elements in Select Element dialog, but it also incurs performance penalty. If your smart package contains a slow-running computation - such as Find - you may want to keep this option off for performance reasons." annotatedElement="cba97780-417c-4831-b91f-bbbc9b5b026f">
